Currently we are providing services to five\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcustomers \u2013 Telenor Bulgaria, Telenor Hungary, Telenor Serbia, Telenor Montenegro and Telenor Global Wholesale (Norway).</p>\n<p class=\"top\">In Telenor, we believe that the successful social strategy of each company begins with responsibility for the people, who build its success and its\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tgood name. For this reason, we provide our staff with the best working\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tconditions to enable them to develop their professional and personal skills.</p>\n<div class=\"tele-block\">\n<div class=\"tele-grad\">\n<div class=\"tele-heading\">\n<h2>Role Overview:</h2>\n</div>\n<!--\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\u0434\u0430 \u043e\u0431\u0438\u0447\u0430\u0448 \u0434\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0434\u0430\u0432\u0430\u0448</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\u0434\u0430 \u0438\u043c\u0430\u0448 \u0430\u043c\u0431\u0438\u0446\u0438\u044f\u0442\u0430 \u0434\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0433\u043d\u0435\u0448 \u043f\u043e\u0432\u0435\u0447\u0435</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\u0434\u0430 \u0441\u0435 \u0432\u044a\u043b\u043d\u0443\u0432\u0430\u0448 \u043e\u0442 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438 \u0442\u0435\u0445\u043d\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0433\u0438\u0438</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\u0434\u0430 \u043e\u0431\u0438\u0447\u0430\u0448 \u0434\u0430 \u043e\u0431\u0449\u0443\u0432\u0430\u0448 \u0441 \u0440\u0430\u0437\u043b\u0438\u0447\u043d\u0438 \u0445\u043e\u0440\u0430</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\u0434\u0430 \u043d\u0435 \u0437\u0430\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0432\u044f\u0448 \u0434\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u043a\u0440\u0435\u043f\u044f\u0448 \u0438 \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u043a\u043e\u043b\u0435\u0433\u0438</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t </ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t -->\n<p class=\"inner\">Telenor Common Operation is looking for a new team member who will be responsible for the configuration and support of the Company\u2019s Billing\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsystems/platforms (Pre/Post-Paid) and for overall activities of the Billing Operations Section in accordance with the Company strategy and SLAs. They offer the full spectrum of financial services, but are also active on the leasing, asset management and factoring markets in Bulgaria.<br/>\r\nKBC Group Bulgaria unites companies with long history and vast experience. UBB was established in 1992 after the merger of 22 Bulgarian regional commercial banks. Following the acquisition of UBB by the Belgian group, the bank received the highest credit rating in Bulgaria, according to Fitch's rating - 'A-', which is higher than the one of Bulgaria. DZI is the company with the longest experience on the Bulgarian insurance market, founded in 1946. Thanks to their excellent distribution network, both companies have branches throughout the country.<br/>\r\nThe companies, part of KBC Group in Bulgaria, serve individual clients, micro businesses, small and medium-sized businesses and corporate clients. They share the vision for digitization and modernization of their activities and services and support the implementation of innovative solutions in their business.<br/>\r\nThe Data Competence Center (part of the Data Science and Automation Directorate) is the Data Science unit of KBC Group Bulgaria. The unit employs various Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence techniques in order to provide advanced data analytics expertise to the business and supporting units of the group.<br/>\n<br/>\r\nMAIN CHALLENGES:<br/>\r\n\u2022Creates and validates advanced data analytics, prediction and decision models<br/>\r\n\u2022Modifies and adjusts existing models<br/>\r\n\u2022Creates documentation for the models<br/>\r\n\u2022Assists in the implementation of the models<br/>\r\n\u2022Participates in the monitoring of the outcomes of the models<br/>\n<br/>\r\nTHE PERFECT CANDIDATE HAS:<br/>\r\n\u2022Strong programming skills, preferably in Python or R. We could also consider candidates with less experience and strong interest in Data Science for a junior position <br/>\r\n\u2022Ability to work in a fast-paced environment, both independently and as a part of a group<br/>\r\n\u2022Entrepreneurial and communicative person with delivery focus<br/>\r\n\u2022Very good command of English, both spoken and written<br/>\r\n\u2022Experience in a financial or insurance institution would be considered as an advantage<br/>\n<br/>\r\nWE OFFER:<br/>\r\n\u2022Career development opportunities in the biggest financial group in Bulgaria<br/>\r\n\u2022United team of motivated and committed professionals<br/>\r\n\u2022Competitive bonus system, tailored to a position\u2019s specifics<br/>\r\n\u2022Opportunities for attending internal and external trainings, as well as such at \u041a\u0412C Group level<br/>\r\n\u2022Comprehensive Medical Care insurance<br/>\r\n\u2022Life Insurance and a health improvement and disease prevention package<br/>\r\n\u2022Preferential terms for use of products and services with all KBC Group companies in Bulgaria<br/>\r\n\u2022Preferential fee for use of a sports card<br/>\r\nIf you wish to become part of our terrific team, please, send us your recent CV and a motivation letter up to 18.09.2019.
